  m_text: "Your grandma needs your help!\n\n<color=#47911f>Collect ingredients</color>
    for the recipe by <color=#47911f>digging</color> around the bushes in the magical
    forest.\n\nBut be careful at <color=#4e56e6>night</color>! <color=#4e56e6>Wolves</color>
    will start <color=#4e56e6>hunting</color> you.\n\nThey\u2019re drawn to light,
    so keep in mind: your <color=#de710b>lantern</color> makes you <color=#de710b>easier
    to spot</color>!"
